Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美波 想留在德国吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果非要留下来 也是可以的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一起去吗…?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也和叶月一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…日本
