Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后经过了一周
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课程也正式开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有习惯日语的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现代国语这门课完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到古文更是只能缴械投降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 吉井君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下haberi的活用形是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是hannari
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你的是古文的活用形态回答却是京都方言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是一目了然的答非所问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 下节课之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把今天学的都复习好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚想着终于能从犹如拷问般的无聊时间中解放出来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛田同学 你去哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说我要回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 一下子没听懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛田同学刚从外国回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是在说外语
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于还没有习惯日语的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不懂他说得那么快的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说尽量努力去理解它了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是脑袋转不过来 快爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙在笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂日语就那么有趣?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在问「中学的时候在什么社团 美波」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这不该现在问的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 这家伙的日语语法对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都不理解我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都这么努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,400)}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,400)}欢迎回来 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 大家都讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,400)}学校怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,400)}非常有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我不应该在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,400)}有交到朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,400)}嗯 交到了很多好朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,400)}真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,400)}嗯 日本真是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,400)}太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是没有融入班级
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂日语 交不到朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有交流的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶性循环
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是第一天的第一印象不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 从写错名字的汉字开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我记得这个写错一直还没改的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 明久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛护中学毕业的人说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上小卖部的面包 来场篮球赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月伙食费很紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下也参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们什么时候关系那么好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tune voudrais pas devenir mon amie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tune voudrais pas devenir mon amie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在说些莫名其妙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂日语
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来monami又是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是叫monami 是美波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连名字都记不住 少跟我装亲近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要和我说话 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 不要嗦哗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 是 男的 你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这么说岛田同学是男的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙连英语都听不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a shit man you are！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说你很烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把生气中的女生说成是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆子不小嘛 明久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 岛田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是觉得岛田的胸部很小是男生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是肘关节好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不懂日语
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部很小的部分却听得非常清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a shit man you are！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太糟糕了 真的是太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不应该来日本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 岛田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是刚认识明久 不是很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋 说不定是个挺有趣的家伙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ba ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说的那句话 去查下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 是说笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tune voudrais pas devenir mon amie
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是在嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查查是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去嘲笑他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tune voudrais pas,Tune voudrais pas……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到相似的单词
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说的到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 日语有这单词吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我的名字都没说对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是monami 是美波的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,monani?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:31.77,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,monami
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:32.95,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,monani
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么都在叫我呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}那不是美波 而是「mon amie」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,400)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\bord1}--美波 3岁 在法国--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法国
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tune voudrais pas devenir mon amie
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是日语啊 更不是德语
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他搞错了 去查了法语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在图书馆里没有把法语直接翻译成德语的字典
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能先翻译成英语 再翻译成德语
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼写也要搞清楚才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然发音也不知道有多少是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tune voudrais pas
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:20:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是英语Could you的初始形态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,devenir
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是become的演变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,monami不是美波
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是mon amie
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英语是my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部翻译出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you become my friend?
